  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the effects of an additional distal rectus femoris
      transfer carried out as a part of single-event multilevel surgery in children with spastic
      diplegic cerebral palsy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
