  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  cerebral palsy

          -  spastic diplegia

          -  ambulatory

          -  stiff knee gait

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  relevant previous surgery at the legs

          -  Botulinum-toxin-injections 6 months prior surgery
      </textblock>
